      "writtenOn": "2020-09-02T18:27:02Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "The original code also used setTimeout over setInterval for the reason of not overloading the servers. Imagine the server is under load and can\u0027t handle the requests fast enough. If the code were setInterval, multiple requests would start stacking up. With setTimeout, we only re-request after our request returns.\n\nI\u0027ll add that decision as a comment.",
